        <footnote id="F1">Class C Google Stock Units (GSU) entitle the Reporting Person to receive one share of Alphabet Inc. Class C capital stock for each share underlying the GSU as GSU vests. 1/18th of the grant will vest on the 25th day of the month starting on March 25, 2025; 1/36th of the grant will vest on the 25th day of each month starting on March 25, 2026; and 1/36th of the grant will vest on March 1, 2027, subject to continued employment on each vesting date.</footnote>
